name: Meridian Executive Limousines
overview:
Meridian Executive Limousine provides executive and private airport car service in Phoenix Arizona.

Meridian Limousines is a limo company and airport transportation provider, authorized by Sky Harbor Airport Phoenix. We are proud to offer professional, on-time, dependable limousine transportation to and from all airports, hotels, golf courses, restaurants, corporate and business centers in Phoenix Metro Area. Our services are available 24 hours a day,7 days a week upon reservation!

Meridian Specializes in:

Executive Limousine Service

Phoenix Airport Car Service

Private Sedan and SUV Transport

FBO Ground Transportation Services

Chauffeured Limousine Services

Point-To-Point Service

Out of Town Services
